  "description": "<i>Conan: &quot;Spotkanie w krypcie&quot;</i> (Conan: Encounter in the crypt) is a short text adventure game, an adaptation of the short story <i>The Thing in the Crypt</i>. Like the original story, the game has young Conan the Barbarian as the protagonist. The game begins as Conan is escaping wolves through the winter; later he finds his way into an old crypt and the mysterious danger awaiting there. <br><br>The game is mostly text, with just the beginning logo and a single picture appearing throughout. ",
